sentences.sentence: In it all tabulations have been rewritten in a consistent style.
sentences.translation: 在它的所有表格中已被重写的一贯作风。

sentences.sentence: More extensive tabulations are available in the engineering data book.
sentences.translation: 更详细的数据可参考《工程数据书》。

sentences.sentence: Many, but not all, tabulations have been revised as a result of a reevaluation of the data.
sentences.translation: 许多人，但不是所有的表格已经修订，由于重新评价的数据。
